This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques to predict the sentiment of songs based on their lyrics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and information retrieval. The paper also uses machine learning algorithms, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves data analysis and classification, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound). Finally, the paper could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) since it involves predicting the sentiment of songs based on their lyrics.
